      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values were compared against the FDA interlaboratory experimental dataset. Mean absolute error across 5 operating points was 9.3%, with maximum deviation of 13.7%. All comparisons fall within the 15% acceptance band specified in project requirements."
