    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2 for this Class II CPB device. The 6 not-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 requirements as documented in the project requirements specification. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met at all 5 evaluated operating points. The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the intended regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
